column16: Jose Constanza grounds out, second baseman Josh Harrison to first baseman Garrett Jones.
Andrelton Simmons flies out to left fielder Alex Presley.
Carlos Gomez hit by pitch.    Jonathan Lucroy to 2nd.
Travis Ishikawa flies out to left fielder Starling Marte.
Jonathan Lucroy singles on a ground ball to second baseman Neil Walker.
Aramis Ramirez lines out to shortstop Jordy Mercer.
Bryan LaHair singles on a ground ball to right fielder Garrett Jones.   Luis Valbuena to 2nd.
Luis Valbuena singles on a ground ball to left fielder Starling Marte.
Ryan Ludwick singles on a sharp ground ball to shortstop Chase d'Arnaud.   Devin Mesoraco scores.    Brandon Phillips to 3rd.
Joey Votto strikes out on a foul tip.
Chris Heisey lines out sharply to left fielder Starling Marte.
Brandon Phillips reaches on a fielder's choice, fielded by catcher Michael McKenry.   Devin Mesoraco to 2nd.
Devin Mesoraco singles on a sharp line drive to left fielder Starling Marte.
